# gap_basic.algo.ct
# Theorem family: Gap membership and CompGap witness recognition.
#
# Scope:
#   Bounded algorithm-form witness for the representative Gap fixtures used by
#   gap_basic.enum.ct and for the depth <= 2 sweep in tests/test_gap.c.
#
# Program:
#   Production i emits 1 followed by the seven-bit binary index i. During the
#   first input-length steps, every head bit equal to 1 appends the certificate
#   for that input position. Head bit 0 appends nothing. The test harness runs
#   exactly input_length steps and compares the remaining tape with the
#   expected positional certificate for that Gap input.
